
Visualizer for hotspots
=========================



Usage
=========================
open hotspots.html with any modern browser that supports HTML5

samples directory contains some sample counters.out files


Libraries
=========================

based on library
http://www.graphdracula.net/

which is a layer on top of http://raphaeljs.com/ (both are MIT licensed)

also uses
jquery
jquery-csv

modifications:
properly draw self pointer edges


